<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_c3533239-b71b-4625-89b1-34479c6fc2ea" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>12.3.4</sptc><title id="_cfcf05cc-67bf-44ea-8bfd-15622cb08a5c">Bracing</title><archive-num>2019: 3.10.6.4</archive-num><subclause id="_7742a5ed-afdf-4dec-abcf-f056a7271f20" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d1c06819-951c-41f2-af00-6ec15ae2edf1">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Where a deck or balcony is more than 1 m off the ground when measured from the uppermost surface of the deck or balcony at any point to the top of any supporting footing, bracing must be installed as follows:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_0d87ddc7-5b69-4f35-b36f-bfa4cdc86bb0">Two diagonally opposed 30 x 0.8 mm galvanized steel straps must be installed across the top or underside of the joists and be attached using one fixing at—<ol><li>each joist or equivalent framing member; and</li><li>the waling plate.</li></ol></li><li id="_8a0c8551-ad36-4c5d-823e-eabed1dfca73">A secondary set of 30 x 0.8 mm steel straps must be installed using one fixing at each joist or equivalent framing member in accordance with <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/904_0.6.0.xml#_a1d8ce46-b1cd-4af5-be8b-53462a130195" id="_da75e28b-43bd-454b-a02d-11526982b5f2" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 12.3.4</xref> where the deck or balcony extends more than 4 m from the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_0b745a31-68c2-46f9-a365-bb26b7fb2fee" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">external wall</xref>.</li><li id="_d16b4c83-1e28-4b5b-935b-ce232ea436f4">The steel straps must—<ol><li>be continuous and extend diagonally at an angle between 30° to 60°; and</li><li>span not more than 4 m when measured along a line at a right angle from the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_df4ac4c9-fb77-4a9d-8c29-2e91f43bedee" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">external wall</xref>.</li></ol></li><li id="_ecae2793-b335-400c-a1d3-13678c565994">Fixings for the steel straps must be—<ol><li>for timber framing, 50 x 3.15 hot-dipped galvanized flat head ring shank or flat head deformed nail; or</li><li>for steel framing, 8-18 self embedding head or wafer head screws.</li></ol></li><li id="_0e2db2f0-c315-4d4c-a2ac-f6fa5ddf6aa8">Where the deck or balcony is located within a severe corrosion environment, the bracing and fixings must comply with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4792_0.14.0.xml#_82b82e0f-9bbf-4ed4-a405-2b9ec229ffda" id="_b58b8eb1-a2e9-4f4f-aeb1-6a6d29e3911f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table 6.3.9a</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4793_0.12.0.xml#_2b6a2e86-5fba-4dd5-b183-c48d81f2ba4a" id="_bcfb9ef3-07d0-424d-9fbb-2f90bb03858d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">6.3.9b</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4852_0.6.0.xml#_29af2ebb-c77f-47fb-903f-41d53a262b97" id="_17392abc-fb11-4d66-a163-22a64dd381f1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">6.3.9c</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/904_0.6.0.xml" id="_a1d8ce46-b1cd-4af5-be8b-53462a130195"><num xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" inv:access="external">12.3.4</num><title xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_e2a47dc3-235d-40f3-9555-595291a7e819" inv:access="external">Bracing of decks and balconies</title><image xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" alt="Bracing of decks and balconies" height="687" heightdpi="200" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:12-3-4-bracing-of-decks-and-balconies.eps" inv:access="external" width="1200" widthdpi="200"/></image-reference></clause>